<html>
    <head>
        <!-- Latest compiled and minified CSS -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">

<link rel="stylesheet" href="index.css">
    </head>
    <body>
        
     <div class="row">
        <div class="col" id="nav">
                <nav class="navbar">
                    <div class="container-fluid">                    
                      <ul class="row nav navbar-nav" >
                        <li class="col-lg-12"><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                        <li class="col-lg-12"><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                        <li class="col-lg-12"><a href="#info">Information</a></li>
                        <li class="col-lg-12"><a href="#info">Guide</a></li>
                      </ul>                      
                    </div>
                  </nav>
            
            
        </div>

        <div class="col" id="main">
          

            <div class="img-div bg-primary" id="home"></div>

            <div id="search"  style="padding-left: 5%;"> 
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                  <h1 class="text-muted" style="font-size: 25px; padding-top: 2%;">Your Searches</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="col">
                  <form class="navbar-form navbar-left" action="/index" method="post">
                    <div class="input-group">
                      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Search" name="search">
                      <div class="input-group-btn">
                        <button class="btn btn-default" type="submit">
                          <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-search"></i>
                        </button>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </form>
                </div>
              </div>  
              <div class="table-responsive-lg" style="overflow-x: auto;">                
                <table class="table table-hover row" >
                  <tr class="row">                    
                    <%obj.forEach((details,index)=>{ %>
                      <td class="col"  style="padding-top: 2%;">
                          <div class="card" style="width:250px">                        
                              <img class="card-img-top" src= "<%= details.track.share.image %>" alt="Card image">
                               <div class="card-body">                                  
                                    <a href="<%= details.track.url %>">
                                      <h4 class="card-title"><%= details.track.title %></h4>
                                    </a>                                                              
                                                                                                                              
                               </div>
                          </div>
                      </td>
                    <% }) %>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div style="padding-left: 5%;">
              <h1 class="text-muted" style="font-size: 25px; padding-top: 2%;">Top Releases</h1>
              <div class="table-responsive-lg" style="overflow-x: auto;">
                <table class="table table-hover row" >
                  <tr class="row">
                    <%releases.forEach((details)=>{ %>
                        <td class="col" style="padding-top: 0.5%;"><div class="card" style="width:250px"><a href="<%= details.url %>">
                          <img class="card-img-top" src= "<%= details.share.image %>" alt="Card image">
                          <div class="card-body">
                            <h4 class="card-title"><%= details.title %></h4>
                          </a>
                          </div></td>                    
                        <% }) %>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>

            <center>
            
                 <!--***********************************CONTACT********************************************************/--> 
                    <div class="row" id="contact" style="height: 80vh;width: 75vw;margin-top: 3vh;">
                      <div class="col-lg-6" id="bg">
                         
                        <h3>Let's Get In Touch<br><p>We are open for any suggestion or just to have a chat</p>
                        <br>
                        <p><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-map-marker"></i>     ADDRESS : 180, West Street ,720 road <br>    New York 124801</p>
                        <p><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-phone"></i> +91 7817070355 </p>
                        <p><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope"></i> Email : b22ai004@iitj.ac.in </p>
                        <p><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-globe"></i> Website : https://roaring-figolla-e4912f.netlify.app/ </p>
                        </h3>
                        
      
                    </div>
                
                
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h1>Drop a message!</h1>
                            <form action="/contact" method="post">
                              <div class="row">
                                <div class="col"><div class="mb-3 mt-3">
                                  <label for="fname" class="form-label">Firstname:</label>
                                  <input type="text" class="form-control" id="fname" placeholder="Enter First Name" name="fname" required>
                                  
                                </div></div>
                                <div class="col"><div class="mb-3 mt-3">
                                  <label for="lname" class="form-label">Lastname:</label>
                                  <input type="text" class="form-control" id="lname" placeholder="Enter Last Name" name="lname" required>
                                  
                                </div></div>
                                
                              </div>
                              
                              <div class="row">
                                <div class="col"><div class="mb-3 mt-3">
                                  <label for="roll" class="form-label">Roll No:</label>
                                  <input type="text" class="form-control" id="roll" placeholder="Enter Roll No" name="roll" required>
                                  
                                </div></div>
                                <div class="col"><div class="mb-3 mt-3">
                                  <label for="email" class="form-label">Email:</label>
                                  <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Email" name="email" required>
      
                                </div></div>
                                
                              </div>
                              <div class="mb-3 mt-3">
                                <label for="comment">Feedback:</label>
                                <textarea class="form-control" rows="5" id="comment" name="text"></textarea>                            
      
                              </div>
                             
                              
                              
                              <div class="submit">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn">Send Message</button>
                              </div>
                              
                            </form>
                          </div>
                    </div>
      
                    </div>
                      
                  
                    <!------------------------------------------INFORMATION-------------------------------------------------->
                    
                    <div class="info" id="info">
                      <div class="row info-text">
                          <div class="col-lg-6"  style="height: 60vh;display: flex;justify-content: center;">
                              <div class="img-bg" style="height: 100%;width: 50%;"></div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="col-lg-6"  style="height: 60vh;">
                              <div class="card-body" style="padding-top: 2%;">
                                  <h4 class="card-title">“Where words fail,<br> music speaks.”</h4>
                                  <p class="card-text author">Welcome to our music discovery website! Here, you can easily search for your favorite music and explore the latest and greatest releases from your favorite artists. Whether you're a music enthusiast, a casual listener, or someone looking for new tunes to add to your playlist, we've got you covered.
                                  </p>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="row info-card" style="margin: 0% 10% 10% 10%;">
                              <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12" style="height: 50vh;background-color: #9417A2;">
                                  <h4 class="card-title">Search and Explore:</h4>
                                  <p class="card-text">Our website provides a user-friendly search feature that allows you to find music by artist, song title, or album name. Simply type in your query, and we'll fetch the most relevant results for you. Whether you're looking for a specific track or want to explore a particular artist's discography, our search functionality will make it easy for you to find what you're looking for.                        </p>
                              </div>
                              <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12" style="height: 50vh;background-color: #A020F0;">
                                  <h4 class="card-title">Top Releases:</h4>
                                  <p class="card-text">Stay up-to-date with the latest trends in the music industry by checking out our "Top Releases" section. We constantly update this section to showcase the hottest songs, albums, and EPs making waves in the music world. From chart-topping hits to rising stars, you'll find a diverse range of music to suit your taste.</p>
                              </div>
                              <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12" style="height: 50vh;background-color: #B24BF3;">
                                  <h4 class="card-title">Music Recommendations:</h4>
                                  <p class="card-text">Discovering new music can be an exciting journey, and we're here to make it even more enjoyable. Our website employs sophisticated algorithms to curate personalized music recommendations based on your listening preferences. Whether you're into rock, pop, hip-hop, electronic, or any other genre, our recommendations will help you explore new artists and genres that align with your musical taste.</p>
                              </div>
                          </div>
                      </div>

            </center>

            
          </div>
        
     </div>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
        
        
        
    </body>
</html>